    menu bar item height based on the current screen's dimensions. This ensures
    oversized icons are scaled down while maintaining their aspect ratio,
    particularly in mixed-DPI environments.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Settings Window Cleanup:</strong> Enhanced the reliability of hiding
    the Dock icon when the settings window is dismissed.
  </li>
